Title: 'A ride make my day '
DateModified: '2019-02-24'
DatePublished: '2019-02-24'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-ride-make-my-day
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Marshal Antony
AuthorCountry: India
Text: The ride make my day. One day when my mood was not good i took my motor bike
  and i went for a ride to munnar and also i am living in kerala the gods own country.
  And i start the ride in early morning and gone by the route moovatupuzha adimaly
  to munnar i was a long ride but it was tremendous i feel positive vibes through
  out the ride and by noon i reached munnar. And i had lunch by 2pm.  And also i have
  my breakfast at kottyam. When i reach munnar it was cool wind blowing and i take
  off my jacket to feel the wind it was feel i cant express and after that i take
  a room for fresh up and i went to some places of munnar. In munnar we can see many
  mountains and greenary and also fresh air because the people in munnar uses mostly
  cycles which cannot cause any pollution. And i enjoy a day at munnar i have my dinnar
  and i went to bed. And by morning i return to home by noon 1.50pm i reach home.
